{
  "texts": [
    "Gaussian process algorithm is employed for performing classification of the OASIS dataset, and Linear Regression is utilized for constructing the model.",
    "ML is used for feature extraction, however, DL yields more precise results.",
    "Similarly, Mathew et al. (2018) devised a method for AD diagnosis through MRI scans.",
    "For classification, probabilistic neural network (PNN), SVM, and kNN are employed.",
    "Approximately 600 images are utilized for training the classifiers."
  ]
}